rem --- The following IOLIST's were removed from this program:

rem --- ivm01a: iolist a0$(1),a1$(1),a2$(1),a3$(1),a4$,a5$,a6$,a[all]
rem --- ivm04a: iolist b0$(1),b1$(1),b2$,b[all]
